{
  "levelId": "sf-05",
  "chapterId": "sf-05",
  "worldId": "sci-fi",
  "title": "漂浮温室：照看星芽",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "garden",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-05.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "漂浮温室里，一颗小星芽正抱着叶子打瞌睡。它需要一点水和一束柔和的光。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是漂浮温室。我们先把“照看星芽”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "care",
          "prompt": "照顾星芽，让它抬起小脑袋。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "浇一滴星水",
              "feedback": "星芽喝饱了，叶子变得亮晶晶。"
            },
            {
              "label": "打开柔光灯",
              "feedback": "柔光落下来，星芽伸了个懒腰。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，浇一滴星水让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘芽’是刚刚长出来的小生命。我们要温柔地照顾它。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "hero",
          "pet"
        ],
